| Issue | Severity | Category | Status |
|-------|----------|----------|--------|
| Exposed Secrets in .env | **CRITICAL** | A07: Identification and Authentication Failures | ❌ Needs Fix |
| No Authentication | **CRITICAL** | A01: Broken Access Control | ❌ Needs Fix |
| Missing Security Headers | **HIGH** | A05: Security Misconfiguration | ❌ Needs Fix |
| No Rate Limiting | **HIGH** | A04: Insecure Design | ❌ Needs Fix |
| No Input Validation | **MEDIUM** | A03: Injection | ⚠️ Preventive |
| No HTTPS | **HIGH** | A02: Cryptographic Failures | ❌ Needs Fix |
| No CORS | **MEDIUM** | A01: Broken Access Control | ❌ Needs Fix |
| No Logging | **MEDIUM** | A09: Logging and Monitoring | ❌ Needs Fix |

---

